(746, 93, 'work_section_title', 'How does it work?'),
(747, 93, '_work_section_title', 'field_629dc5fcc8d5d'),
(748, 93, 'work_section_text', 'The path to sustainabilty includes every one of us! Thats why Ki Futures is an international and holistic program. It brings together the entire cultural sector to face and solve our challenges through co-creation, collaboration, and knowledge exchange.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith coaching, training, workshops, global networking meetings, guest speakers, and more, participants have the opportunity to gain the knowledge and skills needed to implement sustainability in their practices. Participants are encouraged to work together to create international, cross-cultural projects and relationships.'),
