(2203, 166, 'program_section_text', 'Ki Futures empowers organizations and individuals who want to embed sustainability in their practice and inspire their communities.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWere all about collaboration. With Ki Futures, we aim to connect institutions, cultural professionals, and sustainability specialists on a global level, while also engaging with other organizations to develop new tools and resources to spread sustainable practices in the cultural sector.'),
