(3932, 220, 'program_section_text', 'Ki Futures empowers organizations, individuals, companies - all cultural stakeholders to embed sustainability in their practice and inspire their communities.\r\n\r\nKi Futures provides training, workshops, coaches, and an international network of cultural professionals, sustainability specialists, and partner organizations. We provide the critical thinking skills and understanding of sustainability theoretically and work collaboratively to find new paths and solutions for sustainability for culture - on individual, institutional, and sectoral levels. The program provides tangible outcomes through various collective projects as well as support systems to reach individual goals.'),
