(6062, 238, 'works_section_works_data_list_3_text', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The program turns talk into action - providing tangible benchmarks and outputs. It supports participants in creating sustainability initiatives (like green teams) within their organizations and local networks.</p>'),
