(12861, 531, 'ki_toolkit_section_text', 'On the Ki Port, you can find the Ki Toolkit, which houses all of the resources, tools, and links you need for your sustainability journey. The Toolkit includes tailored guides for cultural professionals on sustianbility, a resource center with relevant articles and information, and recordings of all meetings and trainings so you will never miss out. And dont forget to share this with your colleagues to inspire engagement through the entire organization!'),
