(15061, 598, '_works_section_works_data_list_1_image', 'field_629ee24046b79'),
(15062, 598, 'works_section_works_data_list_1_text', '<h6>The program was co-developed with international sustainability and culture experts and draws from real solutions and with inspiration and collaboration from other sectors.</h6>'),
(15063, 598, '_works_section_works_data_list_1_text', 'field_629ee27346b7a'),
(15064, 598, 'works_section_works_data_list_2_image', '91'),
(15065, 598, '_works_section_works_data_list_2_image', 'field_629ee24046b79'),
(15066, 598, 'works_section_works_data_list_2_text', '<h6>The Ki Port streamlines sharing best practices and promotes peer-to-peer learning. Ki Futures cultivates cultures of sustainability within institutions and provides continued support on every level.</h6>'),
(15067, 598, '_works_section_works_data_list_2_text', 'field_629ee27346b7a'),
(15068, 598, 'works_section_works_data_list_3_image', '94'),
(15069, 598, '_works_section_works_data_list_3_image', 'field_629ee24046b79'),
(15070, 598, 'works_section_works_data_list_3_text', '<h6>The program turns talk into action - providing tangible benchmarks and outputs. It supports participants in creating sustainability initiatives (like green teams) within their organizations and local networks.</h6>'),
