(20417, 193, 'ki_port_section_text', 'The Ki Port is our digital platform that powers teams and individuals in the cultural sector to connect with sustainability pioneers around the world. Its a simple, but intuitive, online hub where you will have access to guides and resources, share case studies, participate in live trainings and easily communicate with other members.'),
