(20433, 193, 'project_section_text', 'Ki Futures was designed to help you achieve your sustainability goals. But what if you dont have any yet? In order to ensure progress and tangible outcomes, as well as provide collaborative sectoral movement, every quarter will focus on one Ki Project. These are optional, themed projects that provide objectives and actions.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nProjects for 2022 include Setting Yourself Up for Success: Getting the Most out of Ki Futures and Forming your Team, Energy: Creating Your Baseline and Calculating your Carbon Footprint, SDGs and Policy: A Look at International, Local and Institutional Policy and Documents, and Circular Exhibitions: Designing with Circular Economy Principles.'),
