(20689, 193, 'regional_meeting_section_text', 'Regional Network Meetings (RNM) are monthly meetings with your Coach and other participants in your area. These meetings offer the opportunity for Champions to delve into specific topic discussions, ask questions and brainstorm ideas, participate in peer-to-peer learning and co-creation. RNMs are held in your local language and are the place to develop and execute regional projects. These meetings ensure continuous contact with your Coach and provide local context.'),
