(22714, 193, '_section_5_title', 'field_62a8234319cd4'),
(22715, 193, 'section_5_text', 'Global Network Meetings (GNM) are monthly meetings for all participants from all around the world. Every GNM is an opportunity for Ki Futures participants to connect and collaborate with other champions from other parts of the world. GNMs host guest speakers to present and inspire, provide a platform for participants to present their work and get feedback, and offer networking breakout sessions so Champions can have one-on-one time to get to know colleagues from other parts of the world.'),
